  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dba 24 \u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0da2\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Station masters are on strike for 24 hours",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kasun Chamara, Secretary of the Railway Station Master's Association, said tonight that station masters will leave all services for a period of 24 hours from midnight today (5).",
        "This decision was reached by paying attention to the fact that the station masters have to face the pressure of the people due to the failure of the governing authority to inform the passengers about the running of the trains and protesting the ruling authority's decision to run a few trains only in consultation with the regulatory association. Mr. Kasun Chamara further said that all trains will run to their destination."
      ],
